text:
hi everyone,
I'm trying to build a custom module that has a boolean field and set it up so that when it's toggled on, my Read More button is hidden.

 &lt;script&gt;
        if({{ item.hide_read_more }} === "true"){
           document.getElementById(review-read-more).style.display = "none";
        } else{
           document.getElementById(review-read-more).style.display = "block";
        }
&lt;/script&gt;

{{ item.hide_read_more }} is my boolean
review-read-more is the ID of my Read More button.

any help would be much appreciated
